    "description": "<strong>Power up and swing for the fences in this casual yet chaotic take on an American classic.</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Bad Hop Baseball is a game for one or two players<br></li><li> Two Player Hot-Seat PvP or One Player Against a CPU Opponent<br></li><li> Players take turns taking shots<br></li><li> Players control the power and timing of their swing. After that, it's up to chance!<br></li><li> Each shot generates a Baseball Outcome e.g. out / hit / double / triple / home run<br></li><li> As in baseball, when one side has been put out 3 times, that side is retired for the inning<br></li><li> When one player is retired, the other player will keep batting until they have been put out 3 times as well<br></li><li> The game is 3 innings long<br></li><li> Games cannot end it a tie! Extra innings will continue until a result is reached<br></li><li> In-Game, In-Session, and All-Time stats are saved! Because if there's one thing we baseball fans love, it's STATS.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/616c0d0f2fd98157209ecf046ccb1f46.avif?t=1676946568\" width=616 height=125 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/dedcbca13ecd7eeaf6195404ec26f69e.poster.avif?t=1676946568\" width=550 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/dedcbca13ecd7eeaf6195404ec26f69e.webm?t=1676946568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/dedcbca13ecd7eeaf6195404ec26f69e.mp4?t=1676946568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/b563303b1b9a5ee31add3ccebca3914c.webp?t=1676946568\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/lean_back_and_enjoy.png?t=1676946568\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/37ab51ac5aacafde2903f8949bb0aa0d.poster.avif?t=1676946568\" width=550 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/37ab51ac5aacafde2903f8949bb0aa0d.webm?t=1676946568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/37ab51ac5aacafde2903f8949bb0aa0d.mp4?t=1676946568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/b563303b1b9a5ee31add3ccebca3914c.webp?t=1676946568\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/aca0a3022b5b6c09e65d2428315bc4cf.avif?t=1676946568\" width=616 height=110 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/b563303b1b9a5ee31add3ccebca3914c.webp?t=1676946568\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/a5155cfce48a33512f52aeea6d10a68e.avif?t=1676946568\" width=616 height=133 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/f4ea3921a143a82154cc95a0e715bac4.avif?t=1676946568\" width=616 height